channel.title: [317] Teleport Name
channel.description:
Ok when i press the button 'varrock teleport' it says case: 185 usage: 4140
I created this
[code]sendFrame126("@whi@Home teleport", 4140); sendFrame126("@whi@Home teleport", 185);[/code]
And put it above
[THIS ONES WORKING] [code]sendFrame126("@whi@Mod spell", 1200); sendFrame126("@gre@Requires Modship", 1201);[/code]
But the home teleport name doesnt appear..
Fixed it... it must be 1300 & 1301
